flowchart TB
  Note["<b>Two separate axes</b><br/>Decidability: does a machine halt?<br/>Complexity: how much time or space?"]

  Decidability["<b>Decidability levels</b><br/>Not RE: no recognizer<br/>RE: yes-instances recognized<br/>Recursive: halts on every input"]
  Resources["<b>Resource-bounded decidable classes</b><br/>P: polynomial-time algorithms<br/>NP and co-NP: verifiable certificates<br/>PSPACE = NPSPACE: polynomial space"]
  NPC["<b>NP-complete</b><br/>inside NP<br/>if one NPC problem is in P,<br/>then P = NP"]

  Note --> Decidability
  Note --> Resources
  Resources --> NPC

